1210
01:20:23,280 --> 01:20:26,040
放在锅里 加上一点油就化了 that it used to liquefy in the pan with just a little oil.

1211
01:20:26,210 --> 01:20:28,200
那方法很好 It was a very good system.

1212
01:20:28,450 --> 01:20:30,940
韦力掌管蕃茄汁 Vinnie was in charge of the tomato sauce.

1213
01:20:31,120 --> 01:20:32,520
闻到了没有 Get the smell?

1214
01:20:32,690 --> 01:20:35,420
这肉丸里有三种肉 Three kinds of meat in the meatballs:

1215
01:20:35,590 --> 01:20:37,610
有小牛肉 牛肉和猪肉 Veal beef and pork.

1216
01:20:37,990 --> 01:20:40,080
那好 反正猪肉是一定要的 Good but you gotta have the pork.

1217
01:20:40,260 --> 01:20:41,780
那是主要的味道来源 That's the flavor.

1218
01:20:41,960 --> 01:20:45,420
我觉得他洋葱放多了 但味道还是很好 I felt he used too many onions but it was still a very good sauce.

1219
