那个瘦子警卫越来越令人讨厌了 The skinny guard's getting to be a real pain in the ass.

1245
01:21:56,570 --> 01:21:59,800
- 是该给那个杂种一点教训了 - 我已经摆平了 - We're gonna have to do something. - I took care of him.

1246
01:21:59,970 --> 01:22:01,670
