- 才烤出来的 - 韦力 你的辣椒和洋葱有了 - Fresh. - Vinnie I got your peppers and onions.

1249
01:22:06,080 --> 01:22:08,380
香肠 火腿 还有很多奶酪 Salami prosciutto a lot of cheese.

1250
