1293
01:25:03,360 --> 01:25:05,850
你只要不断把东西带来 All I need is for you is to keep bringing me the stuff.

1294
01:25:06,030 --> 01:25:08,620
这里有个从匹兹堡来的 他会帮我销货 I got a guy in here from Pittsburgh who'll help me move it.

1295
01:25:08,800 --> 01:25:10,520
