1300
01:25:21,440 --> 01:25:22,930
我们只有彼此帮助 We've gotta help each other.

1301
01:25:23,080 --> 01:25:26,740
我们的行动一定要特别特别小心 We've just gotta be really careful while we do it.

1302
01:25:31,420 --> 01:25:33,910
别让我再听到她的名字 I don't want to hear a word about her anymore.

1303
01:25:34,090 --> 01:25:35,110
