01:26:05,920 --> 01:26:09,450
你看到我们的画没有 那张房子和彩虹是我画的 Did you see our pictures? I did the one with the house and rainbow.

1308
01:26:09,620 --> 01:26:11,110
太阳是我画的 I did the sun.

1309
01:26:11,260 --> 01:26:15,160
我的合唱团两星期后有音乐会 你能来吗 My chorus concert is in two weeks. Are you coming?

1310
01:26:16,000 --> 01:26:17,860
喜欢我们的房子吗 Do you like the house?

1311
01:26:19,130 --> 01:26:21,160
凯伦 收拾行李 我们要搬家了 Karen get packed. We're moving out of here.

1312
01:26:21,330 --> 01:26:22,390
怎么搬 With what?

1313
01:26:22,600 --> 01:26:25,700
不用担心 去找新房子就好了 Don't worry with what. Just start looking for a new house.

1314
01:26:25,870 --> 01:26:29,270
明早我要去匹兹堡 那边有几个人欠我一万五千元 I got to go to Pittsburgh in the morning. Those guys there owe me $15000.

1315
01:26:29,440 --> 01:26:31,380
我们没事了 我都安排好了 We'll be all right. I got things lined up.

1316
01:26:31,540 --> 01:26:34,210
匹兹堡 你明天要去向你的假释官报到呀 Pittsburgh? You have to go see your parole officer tomorrow.

1317
01:26:34,380 --> 01:26:37,280
凯伦 不要操心了 一切都会没问题的 Don't worry about it. Everything's gonna be fine.

1318
01:26:37,980 --> 01:26:40,350
- 谁要去保利伯伯家 - 我 - Who wants to go to Uncle Paulie's? - Me!

1319
01:26:50,660 --> 01:26:52,260
你要什么 What do you want?

1320
01:26:52,500 --> 01:26:54,520
甜心 让妈妈好好吃饭 Sweetheart let Mommy eat.

1321
01:26:58,000 --> 01:27:00,870
气色不错 牢里有吃得这么好吗 You look good. Did you eat this good in the joint?

1322
01:27:03,010 --> 01:27:04,870
不要再搞那些勾当了 I don't want any more of that shit.

1323
01:27:05,050 --> 01:27:06,030
什么勾当 What shit?

1324
01:27:06,210 --> 01:27:08,810
- 离那些垃圾远一点 - 保利 - Just stay away from the garbage. - Look Paulie...

